   [bullet.gif] Research and Training Opportunities at the National
   Institutes of Health
   This site, sponsored by the NIH Office of Education, lists
   opportunities at the high school through the postdoctoral level.
   Clinical training and tenure-track openings are also listed.
   [bullet.gif] NIH Research Training and Career Development Opportunities
   This site, sponsored by the NIH Office of Extramural Research, lists
   both extramural (at institutions across the United States) and
   intramural (at the NIH) training programs for high school students,
   college students, postbaccalaureate students and postdoctoral trainees.
